## ğŸ§° Requirements

- Python 3.7+
- Git installed

---

## ğŸ§ª Installation

Install via pip:

```bash
pip install commitly-cli 
````

Or clone it locally:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Tostenn/commitly-cli.git
cd commitly-cli
python main.py --help
```

> Make sure [`commitly`](https://github.com/Tostenn/commitly) is also installed:
>
> ```bash
> pip install commitly
> ```

