### ğŸ§± Large commit with consistency

```bash
commitly-cli \
  --add . \
  --style formal.txt \
  --format conventional.txt \
  --recommandation rules.txt \
  --ticket "#88" \
  --push \
  --confirm
```

> Maintain consistency across big code changes like a pro ğŸ’¼

